# Extra deletion targets for clean.sh (scripts/clean.py), gitignore-style globs.
# clean.sh already removes CACHEDIR.TAG-tagged dirs, .venv/venv, __pycache__,
# *.pyc/*.pyo and .DS_Store automatically; list anything else here. Source files
# (*.py, *.sh, *.md) and VCS (.git) are protected and never removed.
#
# NOTE: the RFC cache lives in ~/.cache/rfc-skill/, not in this repo — empty it
# with `python3 rfc/scripts/rfc_tool.py --clear-cache`, not with clean.sh.

*.skill
*.zip
*.egg-info
